se-fix</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T17:33:21-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T17:33:21-04:00</updated><title> WordPress 商标和开源之争的最新进展</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;WordPress 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zMD36VxriYMcQhvrLlQ1tG03fAY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73632750/STK302_WORDPRESS.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;WordPress 及其联合创始人 Matt Mullenweg 卷入了与第三方托管提供商 WP Engine 的公开斗争。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262410/wordpress-fight-trademarks-open-source-mullenweg&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262410/wordpress-fight-trademarks-open-source-mullenweg" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262410/wordpress-fight-trademarks-open-source-mullenweg</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T16:33:16-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T16:33:16-04:00</updated><title>最适合训练和日常生活的 Garmin 手表</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;彩色背景上的几款 Garmin 手表&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D5dtgeyIVuFtgCeI1hMNSF_9Epo=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72245384/236645_Buying_Guide_Garmin_Watches_WJoel.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Garmins 不再只是多项运动的庞然大物。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Will Joel / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Garmin 可能以其硬核健身手表而闻名，但它也提供广泛的生活方式产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T16:30:32-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T16:30:32-04:00</updated><title> MKBHD 的壁纸应用程序更新，广告更少</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Marques Brownlee 在打开面板应用程序的情况下举起手机的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hv1S8Xum4QEz5VYdTE-Ash-NAdE=/182x0:2234x1368 /1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73632643/panels_app_update.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图像：MKBHD &lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www .youtube.com/watch?v=MRtg6A1f2Ko&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;来自 YouTube&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;h3a0HU&quot;>;MKBHD 的新壁纸应用程序在发布后收到了首次重大更新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/24/24253023/mkbhd-panels-wallpaper-app-response-criticism&quot;>;用户批评该应用的定价&lt;/a>;和广告设置免费帐户。周五，&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/panels_art/status/1842227074284536287?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1842227074284536287%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;amp;ref_url=about% 3Asrc文档&quot;>;Panels 帐户在 X 上宣布&lt;/a>;，免费使用该应用程序的用户现在可以通过观看单个广告来下载高分辨率图像，而不仅仅是标清图像。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1CFTaR&quot; >;该应用程序之前要求用户每月支付 11.99 美元（或每年 49.99 美元）订阅才能访问全分辨率图像。它还要求免费用户在下载标清壁纸之前观看两个广告。此后，Panels 取消了这一要求，现在允许用户下载标清图像而不会看到广告。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;peHhfD&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; data-dnt=&quot;true&quot;align =&quot;center&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;主要更新 #1：我们一直专注于应用程序...&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262350/mkbhd-panels-wallpaper-app-fewer-ads-update&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262350/mkbhd-panels-wallpaper-app-fewer-ads-update" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262350/mkbhd-panels-wallpaper-app-fewer-ads-update</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T15:45:43-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T15:45:43-04:00</updated><title>从 AOL 时代华纳到 DirecTV 和 Dish：20 年的媒体合并</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一美元钞票经过 Photoshop 处理，上面有 Dish、DirecTV 和 AOL 时代华纳的徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Y5G_geOjH5FpL51TZkEx0kYq0H8=/275x274:1713x1233/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73632542/247300_ONE_DOLLAR_MERGER_ CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jkvZn9&quot;>;本周，DirecTV &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/30 /24258196/directv-dish-merger-tpg-deal-announcement&quot;>;宣布打算以一美元收购 Dish、Sling TV&lt;/a>; 以及 EchoStar 的其余电视业务（同时还承担 Dish 的所有债务） ，这两家公司的近 2000 万卫星电视订户合并了数十年。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uibRD3&quot;>;但不仅仅是 DirecTV 和 Dish。多年来，AT&amp;T、康卡斯特、威瑞森、通用电气、通用汽车、新闻集团、Tumblr 以及时代华纳的各个化身在试图弥合通信和媒体之间的鸿沟时也被混合或分裂。&lt;/p >; &lt;p id=&quot;zEe6u2&quot;>;以下是可能以这两家公司最终合并而结束的事件的部分时间表。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;7VkP7o&quot;>;AOL，会见时代华纳&lt;/h2>; &lt; p id=&quot;0S4vsx&quot;>;在 21 世纪之交，互联网显然......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/ 4/24259360/directv-dish-merger-timeline-aol-timewarner&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24259360/directv-dish-merger-timeline-aol-timewarner" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24259360/directv-dish-merger-timeline-aol-timewarner</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T15:29:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T15:29:53-04:00</updated><title>最好的预算机器人真空吸尘器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种扫地机器人插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HibcNT_fQEjjbn2ocPGsJMt6h-E=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72624795/Best_Robot_vaccum_cleaners_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;您不必花一大笔钱让机器人清洁您的地板。这是我们精选的您现在可以购买的最具成本效益的机器人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-拖把&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-mop" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-mop</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T14:25:33-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T14:25:33-04:00</updated><title> Matt Mullenweg：“WordPress.org 只属于我”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Matt Mullenweg 在 WordCamp 的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eP1oZvxx0QUcuwnNH3gekkuVwpI=/160x0:2065x1270/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73632344/mullenweg_eu_wordcamp.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Matt Mullenweg 在欧洲 2024 年 WordCamp 上。&lt;/em>; |图片：WordCamp&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;WordPress 开源项目、支持该项目的非营利组织以及 Automattic 旗下的商业部门之间的界限正在变得模糊。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262232/matt-mullenweg-wordpress-org-wp-engine&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262232/matt-mullenweg-wordpress-org-wp-engine" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262232/matt-mullenweg-wordpress-org-wp-engine</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-04T13:54:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-04T13:54:53-04:00</updated><title> Arc 的“更好的移动浏览器”现已在 Android 上推出</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉色和蓝色背景上的弧形标志。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/py8hFArIQM160c_UB8tkdEaV9Cs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73632264/STK283_ARC_BROWSER_D.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uKiSzw&quot;>;经过几个月的等待，现在 Android 用户可以试用 Arc Search 应用程序。经过开发者的调侃&lt;a href=&quot;之后，现在它在 Google Play 商店中&lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/apps/testing/company.thebrowser.arc&quot;>;以公开测试版形式提供&lt;/a>; https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/23/24226870/arc-is-coming-to-android-soon&quot;>;8 月份推出该应用的 Android 版本&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;PAAht9&quot;>;Arc 是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23462235/arc-web-browser-review&quot;>;浏览器公司对网络浏览的看法&lt;/a>;，将自己标榜为产品比竞争对手更好的定制选项。 Arc Search 应用程序还配备了一项名为“为我浏览”的人工智能功能，可以在网络上搜索您的查询，并根据其来源提供摘要。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;BktnHf&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;研究人员揭示了 Arc 浏览器中的&#39;灾难性&#39;安全漏洞&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/20/24249919/arc-browser -boost-firebase-vulnerability-patched&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Arc 浏览器添加安全公告和错误赏金&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24256271/ arc-browser-bug-bounty-security-bulletin&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;uVIljm&quot;>;该应用程序还会自动存档旧标签页，默认情况下会阻止广告，并摆脱了数据跟踪弹出窗口，这让我想放弃 Edge。虽然 Arc 最初是作为 Mac 专用桌面浏览器推出的，但 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/28/24053882/arc-search-browser-web-app-ios&quot;>;Arc搜索应用&lt;/a>;广泛推出...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262056/arc-search-android-beta-mobile -web-browser&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262056/arc-search-android-beta-mobile-web-browser" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262056/arc-search-android-beta-mobile-web-browser</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>